channel.title: The Dengineers
channel.desc: Mark and Lauren get the help of experts to design dream dens for children. Cooking eggs since he joined his adoptive dads at the age of seven, 11-year-old Nathan has turned up the heat and wants to be a chef. Of course, every chef needs a kitchen, but Nathan can never get into his as his dad is always using it as a workshop. So he is after a kitchen hangout in his back garden where he has space to whip up his own culinary creations.
